立法會普選，雖然距離立法會選舉的時間已經不多但至少我們亦應嘗試實現人權與民主法案中有關2020香港普選的內容，至少也應與美方得出一個可行的普選藍圖！<br />\n<br />\n不自由，毋寧死！香港人在過去大半年已展示出對爭取民主的決心，希望三位泛民議員亦可與香港人並肩而行，在&quot;美港交流會&quot;上表達對真普選的熱切渴求﹕實施真普選、取消功能組別！最後，僅祝三位身體健康、工作順利！<br />\n</strong></strong><br />\n<strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n一位熱心的香港人敬上</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2c561666d5dfe8a4aa592a836b5da403423be81b","tid":1914658,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a33eb834b0bb8be60b97eba62b8a63f90a9f4d6","tid":1914658,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"剛剛sd 左"},{"pid":"c10e14bde6b7389b95df50eae2648661caa3dea3","tid":1914658,"uid":339472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a33eb834b0bb8be60b97eba62b8a63f90a9f4d6","tid":1914658,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"剛剛sd 左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"感謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c268d88a1709f5963ba8a1e2ec4a22af611156c7","tid":1914658,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f02f235b847541a98eec871ab8a92c4e180dbccc","tid":1914658,"uid":290739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38cc919e63381c68f09777e59d3670e35c489e44","tid":1914658,"uid":339472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5acdb5a24a4ed397ffcd000559ce5ed904488b7","tid":1914658,"uid":290739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"我要雙普選呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"